'''''Soleil Ô''''' ( [sɔ.lɛj o] ; "Oh, Sun") ni filime yikinamico yo  mu gifaransa-Mauritanian yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Med Hondo<ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/30299-soleil</ref> .

== Umugambi ==
Filime ''Soleil'' , yakozwe mu myaka ine n’ingengo y’imari iciriritse cyane, ivuga amateka y’umwimukira w'umwirabura winjiye i Paris ashakisha “abakurambere be ba Gaul”<ref>https://www.newyorker.com/goings-on-about-town/movies/soleil-o-oh-sun</ref>. Iyi manifeste ya firime iramagana ivangura: Abimukira bashaka cyane akazi n’aho baba<ref>https://face-foundation.org/soleil-o/</ref>, ariko ugasanga imbonankubone batitaweho, bakangwa, kandi bagasuzugurwa, mbere yo kumvira umuhamagaro wa nyuma wo kwigomeka<ref>https://www.festival-cannes.com/en/films/soleil-o</ref>.

Umutwe werekeza ku ndirimbo yo mu Burengerazuba bw'Ubuhinde ivuga ububabare bw'abirabura bo muri Dahomey (ubu ni [[Bene|Bénin]] ) bajyanywe muri Karayibe nk'abacakara.

