== Kugarura ==
Muri 2017, ''Soleil'' given yahawe gusanwa na Cineteca di Bologna ayobowe na Med Hondo. Inkunga yaturutse mu muryango wa George Lucas Family Foundation n'Umushinga wa Sinema ku Isi, mu rwego rwo gusana aba nyuma bise umushinga ndangamurage w'Afurika<ref>https://www.janusfilms.com/films/1978</ref>.
